Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.92,0:02:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（记录现任女教师）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.32,0:02:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（某天一支带子寄到BeFree）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.76,0:02:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（看着带了里收录的画面吓了一跳）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.04,0:03:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.44,0:04:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（收录的是男女在教室搞的画面）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.08,0:04:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（和这个寄件者-RYU接触）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.72,0:04:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（和RYU用MAIL连络约在酒吧见面）\N（本以为叫RYU的人会很凶，可是...）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.84,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，等很久了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.88,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,MAIL的那个人?...对，我是RYU\N（RYU， 某私立高中教）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.96,0:04:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到是女性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.60,0:04:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那支带子是在哪来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.04,0:05:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那支带子是我拍的...你拍的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.56,0:05:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超赞，那样子很不容易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很简单啊，只要有人就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.12,0:05:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然这么说，好赞...觉得如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.28,0:05:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我超兴奋的...太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.68,0:05:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其它还有吗?..要拍当然可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.72,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么容易就可以拍?...可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请让我拍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.12,0:05:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是得要学校没人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.12,0:06:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时再和你连络吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了，等你连络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.08,0:06:17.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（等连络一个星期）\N（试着去她说的学校看看）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.32,0:12:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（没想到和学生SEX的是本人）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.64,0:12:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我就在不知道情况下协助了）\N（后来为了说服他约了再见面）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.32,0:12:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（在制作事务所）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思，久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.40,0:12:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到竟然是你本人上场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.56,0:12:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓到了吗?...是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.32,0:13:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了，那我就全说出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.80,0:13:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我是那学校的老师\N那孩子则是我的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.00,0:13:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都觉得很无趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.24,0:13:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为求刺激我就诱惑了学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后便在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.84,0:13:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和老师搞，学生也很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.28,0:13:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是很开心，可是还想要更刺激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.96,0:13:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就自己偷拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.04,0:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要刺激啊?可是怎么会偷拍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.64,0:14:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要更兴奋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是变态女老师啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就让我拍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.32,0:14:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这么说\N没差啦，反正你也想拍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.20,0:14:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吧!?一下就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.56,0:14:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要被摸吧!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着镜头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舌头再出来点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.32,0:16:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要怎么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以解开吧！?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.40,0:17:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.68,0:17:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.04,0:17:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有爽吗?说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:18:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用力点?这样子?...再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.64,0:20:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道这个吗?...知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.96,0:20:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.48,0:22:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以直接吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.84,0:22:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接会更好的...要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.56,0:22:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.72,0:22:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.68,0:22:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.44,0:23:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.00,0:23:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再多一根吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.80,0:23:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去吗?...想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.64,0:23:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就来好好帮你用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.20,0:24:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去...真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.36,0:24:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.28,0:24:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插入咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.60,0:24:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.08,0:24:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.88,0:25:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.76,0:25:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.08,0:25:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.64,0:25:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:57.96,0:26:02.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.40,0:26:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:33.80,0:26:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.48,0:26:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得好怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:02.60,0:27:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.00,0:27:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得好怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.32,0:27:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看一下里头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:49.16,0:27:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:15.40,0:28:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很赞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:25.32,0:28:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.88,0:28:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以找学生出来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.04,0:28:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自拍你们搞的样子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:44.52,0:28:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是学生不知道我偷拍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:50.28,0:28:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没差啦，就叫他拍啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.08,0:29:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我用的话，你能答应我件事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.72,0:29:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗?那好啊，要做什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:11.24,0:29:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.32,0:29:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（吓到了，这女老师真好色）\N（真期待搞时是什么表情呢?）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:32.84,0:29:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得师生SEX如何?...好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:42.76,0:29:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看那个，是摄影机哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.00,0:29:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用那个来自拍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.44,0:29:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:08.36,0:33:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:27.56,0:39:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.08,0:40:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:39.40,0:42:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.20,0:46:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了，来插吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:00.68,0:47:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:44.68,0:47:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:12.36,0:49:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:00.68,0:50:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:59.88,0:51:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:47.40,0:52:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:32.20,0:54:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:37.64,0:54:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:08.68,0:56:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行，好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:15.56,0:56:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:13.16,0:57:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:17.80,0:57:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:51.56,0:57:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以射吗?...中出老师吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:55.72,0:57:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗?...射吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:04.68,0:58:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:08.68,0:59:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（应她要求在放假的教室里）\N（拍和职业的AV男提高）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:17.16,0:59:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真怀念呢...很久没来学校?...是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:22.92,0:59:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会来拍吗?\N现在可是很兴奋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:29.32,0:59:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么兴奋啊?...因为之前没遇真货啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:38.60,0:59:41.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:43.72,0:59:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，我是男优松尾...我叫江波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:49.80,0:59:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好，今天请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:53.00,0:59:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真性感的样子，都这样上课的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:58.44,0:59:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:06.28,1:00:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,RYU，太好色的样子了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:11.08,1:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教师竟然这么好色
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:14.92,1:00:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就开始了哦，老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.36,1:00:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:29.16,1:00:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师到那里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:48.84,1:00:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以弄了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:38.76,1:02:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好色了吧，老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:09.80,1:03:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:31.24,1:03:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真变态啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:40.52,1:03:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在教空搞有兴奋吗? ...超兴奋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:58.92,1:04:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好好用奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:08.52,1:04:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好软
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:16.84,1:04:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师都在这里上课的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:22.92,1:04:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都在这里上课的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:28.84,1:04:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:39.40,1:04:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，力道可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:50.92,1:04:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要再多一点吗?...再用力点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:57.16,1:05:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:18.28,1:06:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师如何?...好有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:23.56,1:06:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吗...好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:32.20,1:06:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很赞是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:50.44,1:06:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:21.32,1:07:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我摸穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:02.12,1:08:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用穴吧!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:13.00,1:08:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:05.48,1:09:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:41.96,1:09:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:27.56,1:10:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:45.96,1:10:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:54.76,1:10:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:10.60,1:11:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,者师很爽吧!?下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:17.31,1:11:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手撑那里，屁股翘好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:24.84,1:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师看这里哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:34.76,1:11:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.28,1:11:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穴被这么弄如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:58.60,1:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.08,1:12:04.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:15.88,1:12:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:24.68,1:12:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:26.60,1:12:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:41.80,1:12:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.68,1:12:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:08.20,1:13:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎变这么湿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:18.12,1:13:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来舔我的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:35.24,1:13:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用那好色的舌头舔奶头
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:40.68,1:13:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.04,1:14:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:24.68,1:14:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:38.60,1:14:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸得真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:57.32,1:14:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:12.84,1:15:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:27.56,1:15:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:10.28,1:16:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何啊?...好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:32.52,1:16:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:25.48,1:17:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，起来翘好屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:42.76,1:17:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:23.40,1:18:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:27.24,1:18:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:33.32,1:18:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师来奶炮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:39.08,1:18:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是超湿的，爽这湿老二吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:54.12,1:18:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:09.96,1:19:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的奶摩起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:14.92,1:19:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:52.68,1:19:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:09.48,1:20:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，来深含吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:18.92,1:20:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:25.00,1:20:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:45.32,1:20:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超赞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:40.36,1:21:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好含啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:45.00,1:21:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师深含没问题嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:02.28,1:22:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:15.24,1:22:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:18.76,1:22:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:59.08,1:23:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽，好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:20.84,1:24:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超赞的老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:15.24,1:25:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽...老二好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:22.12,1:26:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以后面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:26.76,1:26:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面插我吧...那来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:40.68,1:26:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手撑好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:53.00,1:26:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:03.72,1:27:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，看好屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:08.84,1:27:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:13.96,1:27:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，好清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:30.28,1:27:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:57.48,1:27:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:39.08,1:28:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:04.84,1:29:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背撑起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:20.36,1:29:21.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:41.80,1:29:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:49.80,1:30:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:52.84,1:30:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超赞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:59.08,1:31:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:05.80,1:31:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:42.60,1:31:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:07.08,1:32:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么很好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:09.16,1:33:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下去咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:14.76,1:33:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手用好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:26.44,1:33:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超爽的...是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:49.32,1:33:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽...这么爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:08.52,1:34:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:40.04,1:34:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，上桌子去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:56.36,1:34:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真下流的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:54.76,1:35:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:28.36,1:36:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师起来看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:13.00,1:37:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插好深啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:15.88,1:37:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这插如何?...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:37.00,1:38:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:46.76,1:38:48.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:53.96,1:38:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，用力咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:08.04,1:39:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:00.20,1:40:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:18.44,1:40:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:01.96,1:41:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:10.76,1:41:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来师，快射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:15.40,1:41:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:37.16,1:41:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，吸干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:44.20,1:41:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:41:49.96,1:41:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都用光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:31.56,1:42:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:38.92,1:42:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣在是好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:58.76,1:43:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（拍摄后几天找老师来制作事务所）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:06.92,1:43:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（在这天我才知道老师惊讶的真面目）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:15.88,1:43:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我本是像往常般拍着素人摄影）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:28.04,1:43:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（在制作事务师）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:35.08,1:43:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师，和职业的AV男优如何啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:47.08,1:43:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超兴奋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:51.72,1:43:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是还有些想用弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:58.44,1:44:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是只有肉体在爽而多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:06.28,1:44:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很希望能连心里都爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:11.40,1:44:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么所以还在努力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:16.68,1:44:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为男人很傻啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:22.12,1:44:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为主导自己身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:29.00,1:44:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟个小鬼似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:39.56,1:44:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没试过你哦，就让我来试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:32.84,1:45:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:51.24,1:47:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要舔咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:16.84,1:52:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用奶来弄哦，可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:08.04,1:53:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:53:31.72,1:53:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超软的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:55.72,1:54:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗?...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:50.60,1:57:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:32.52,1:58:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经射了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:42.28,1:58:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:48.68,1:58:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无趣的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:53.00,1:58:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
